<html ><head ><meta charset="UTF-8"  /><meta name="author" content="Martin Walther - @tinuwalther"  /><meta name="keywords" content="Pode, PSHTML, PowerShell, Mermaid Diagram"  /><meta name="description" content="Builds beatuifull HTML-Files with PSHTML from native PowerShell-Scripts"  /><link rel="stylesheet" href="\assets\BootStrap\bootstrap.min.css"  /><link rel="stylesheet" href="\assets\style\style.css"  /><script src="\assets\BootStrap\bootstrap.bundle.min.js"  ></script><title >#PSXi Pode Server</title><link rel="icon" href="/assets/img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon"  /></head><Body ><header ><div Style="padding:15; background-color:#033b63" Id="j1" Class="jumbotron text-center"  ><p ><h1 >#PSXi Pode Server</h1></p><p >I ♥ PS Pode > This is an example for using pode and PSHTML, requested by API</p></div></header><Section Id="section"  ><nav Class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark navbar-dark sticky-top"  ><div Class="container-fluid"  ><a Target="_self" href="/" Class="navbar-brand"  >»HOME</a><button Class="navbar-toggler" data-bs-target="#collapsibleNavbar" data-bs-toggle="collapse" type="button"  ><span Class="navbar-toggler-icon"  ></span></button><div Id="collapsibleNavbar" Class="collapse navbar-collapse"  ><ul Class="navbar-nav"  ><li Class="nav-item dropdown"  ><button Class="nav-link dropdown-toggle btn btn-sm-outline" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown"  >Pode</button><ul Class="dropdown-menu bg-dark navbar-dark"  ><li Class="dropdown-item bg-dark navbar-dark"  ><a Target="_self" href="#InstallPode" Class="nav-link"  >Install Pode</a></li><li Class="dropdown-item bg-dark navbar-dark"  ><a Target="_self" href="#ConfigurePode" Class="nav-link"  >Configure Pode</a></li><li Class="dropdown-item bg-dark navbar-dark"  ><a Target="_self" href="#StartPode" Class="nav-link"  >Start Pode</a></li></ul></li><li Class="nav-item"  ><a Target="_blank" href="https://badgerati.github.io/Pode/" Class="nav-link"  >Pode docs</a></li><li Class="nav-item"  ><a Target="_self" href="/help" Class="nav-link"  >Help</a></li></ul></div></div></nav><div Id="Content" Class="Container"  ><article Id="Pode"  ><h1 Style="color:#212529"  >Pode</h1><p Style="color:#000"  >Pode is a Cross-Platform framework to create web servers that host REST APIs, Web Sites, and TCP/SMTP Servers.</p><p Style="color:#000"  >It also allows you to render dynamic files using .pode files, which is effectively embedded PowerShell, or other Third-Party template engines. 
                            Pode also has support for middleware, sessions, authentication, and logging; as well as access and rate limiting features. 
                            There's also Azure Functions and AWS Lambda support!</p><p Style="color:#000"  >Pode and Pode.web is created by Matthew Kelly <a Target="_blank" href="https://github.com/Badgerati"  >(Badgerati)</a>, licensed under the MIT License.</p><h2 Style="color:#212529" Id="InstallPode"  >How to install pode</h2><p Style="color:#000"  >You can install pode from the PowerShell-Gallery.</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Install-Module -Name Pode -Verbose</pre><h2 Style="color:#212529" Id="ConfigurePode"  >How to configure pode</h2><p Style="color:#000"  >Create a root folder, for example PodePSHTML:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >New-Item -Path . -Name PodePSHTML -ItemType Directory -Force -Confirm:$false</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Change in to the new directory:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Set-Location ./PodePSHTML</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Clone the code from my repository:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >git clone https://github.com/tinuwalther/PodePSHTML.git</pre><h2 Style="color:#212529" Id="StartPode"  >How to start pode</h2><p Style="color:#000"  >Open a PowerShell and enter:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >pwsh ./PodePSHTML/PodeServer.ps1</pre></article></div></Section></Body><div Style="background-color:#343a40" Class="container-fluid"  ><footer ><div Class="container-fluid"  ><div Class="row align-items-center"  ><div Class="col-md"  ><p ><a Target="_self" href="#" Class="btn-sm btn btn-outline-success"  >I ♥ PS ></a></p></div><div Class="col-md"  ><p >Based on <a Target="_blank" href="https://www.powershellgallery.com/packages/Pode"  >pode</a> and <a Target="_blank" href="https://www.powershellgallery.com/packages/PSHTML"  >PSHTML</a></p></div><div Style="color:#000" Class="col-md"  ><p >Created at 2024-07-16 20:22:44</p></div></div></div></footer></div></html>
